title: Ennai Kollathey Lyrics Geethaiyin Radhai
stanzas: <div>Ennai Kollathey Song Lyrics Geethaiyin Radhai

Ennai kollathe
thalli poogaathe
nenjai killaathe
Kanmani..

Sonna en sollil
illai unmaigal
yeno kobangal
Solladi..

Unnai theendaamal
unnai paarkaamal
Konji peesamal
kannil thookkamillai

Ennul nilee vanthaal
nenjil vaazhginraai
Vittu chellaathe
ithu niyaayamillai..

Kannal moodi kondaalum
unnai kanden.
Meendum yaenintha yaekkam.

Vellai mega thundukkul
Ezhum minnal pol
Enthan vaazhvengum minnaal..

En ithazh melindru
vaazhum maunangal
En manam pesuthe
nooru ennangal

Sonna sollin arthanggal
ennul vaazhuthe
Thooram thalli chendraalum
uyir theeduthe..

Asai vaarthai ellame
indru kiiralaai
Enthan nenjin oorathil
paaya seigiraai..

Ennul nil vanthaai
innum vaazhginraai
Unthan sollaale
thooram undaakkinaai

Ennai theendaathe
ennai paarkaathe
Onrum pesaathe
pothum thunbangal..

Ennai vittu sellaathe
enthan anbe
Vendum un kaathal
ondrey.

Unnai mattum nesithen
ithu unmai
Innum yaenintha oodal..

En uyirkaathalai
unthan kaathoram
Orumuraiyaavathu solla
nee vendum

Enthan aasai muthangal
unnai serumo
Illai kaathal yuthangal
innum neelumo..

Unthan kannil nee sindhum
eeram yenadi
Nenjin baaram veendaame
ennai paaradi..

Ennai kollathe
thalli poogaathe
nenjai killaathe
Kanmani..

Sonna en sollil
illai unmaigal
yeno kobangal
Solladi..
